text: Darlene Ramdin (born 5 August 1989) is a Trinidad and Tobago female volleyball player. She was part of the Trinidad and Tobago women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2017 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. She played for St. John's University's women's volleyball team. == References == ==Other websites== * Darlene set to settle unfinished business , Volleyverse, October 23, 2017 Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Trinidad and Tobago volleyball players
